title: Scooby Doo - Legend of the Vampire
description:
On vacation in Australia, Scooby and the gang attend a music contest held at Vampire Rock---where the legendary &#039;Yowie Yahoo&#039; Vampire is kidnapping the musical acts, including the Hex Girls. Masquerading as heavy-metal band &#039;Those Meddling Kids,&#039; Scooby and the others must discover the identity of the Vampire&#039;s minions. Written by T.
